00:08:26.586 --> 00:08:28.460 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: What was the
motivation behind that?

00:08:28.460 --> 00:08:30.660 align:middle line:84%
>>BALL: The motivation
was to isolate CO2

00:08:30.660 --> 00:08:32.429 align:middle line:90%
