false information, by the way.

00:08:37.549 --> 00:08:40.150 align:middle line:90%
He says, the highest level ever.

00:08:40.150 --> 00:08:42.289 align:middle line:84%
In fact, it's at
the lowest level

00:08:42.289 --> 00:08:44.600 align:middle line:90%
in a very, very long time.

00:08:44.600 --> 00:08:47.480 align:middle line:84%
And by that, I mean
in 300 million years.

