But they wanted to demonize CO2.

00:09:36.800 --> 00:09:39.180 align:middle line:84%
And the reason that they
did that was-- actually it

00:09:39.180 --> 00:09:42.950 align:middle line:84%
goes back to, not about climate
change or global warming

00:09:42.950 --> 00:09:43.940 align:middle line:90%
at all.

