and as it industrializes, it
uses more and more resources

00:09:55.760 --> 00:09:58.840 align:middle line:84%
and that will ultimately
run out of resources.

00:09:58.840 --> 00:10:00.770 align:middle line:10%
That was encapsulated
in that book

00:10:00.770 --> 00:10:03.300 align:middle line:10%
by the Club of Rome,
