00:37:34.460 --> 00:37:38.890 align:middle line:84%
How dangerous is it for science
to keep pushing this agenda

00:37:38.890 --> 00:37:42.170 align:middle line:84%
that man-made climate
change is the cause for all

00:37:42.170 --> 00:37:42.970 align:middle line:90%
these problems?

00:37:42.970 --> 00:37:45.850 align:middle line:84%
>>BALL: I think the
credibility of science

00:37:45.850 --> 00:37:50.110 align:middle line:84%
is in serious trouble, not just
because of the climate issue.

00:37:50.110 --> 00:37:55.010 align:middle line:84%
You know-- it started by
the way in court cases,

00:37:55.010 --> 00:37:57.615 align:middle line:84%
and the first scientists
were the psychiatrists.

00:37:57.615 --> 00:37:58.990 align:middle line:84%
And they'd get
one that would say

00:37:58.990 --> 00:38:01.114 align:middle line:84%
the guy's sane and the
other one to say he's crazy.

00:38:01.114 --> 00:38:02.935 align:middle line:90%
Well, aren't they scientists?

00:38:02.935 --> 00:38:03.735 align:middle line:90%
Don't they agree?

00:38:03.735 --> 00:38:06.010 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Find some
middle ground here.

00:38:06.010 --> 00:38:09.670 align:middle line:84%
>>BALL: Now, what you're seeing
is, oh, butter's bad for you.

00:38:09.670 --> 00:38:11.410 align:middle line:84%
Now butter's good
for you. [INAUDIBLE]

00:38:11.410 --> 00:38:12.710 align:middle line:90%
is good for you, now had.

00:38:12.710 --> 00:38:15.540 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Margarine was
good for you, now it's not.

00:38:15.540 --> 00:38:18.215 align:middle line:84%
>>BALL: And so the whole
credibility of science

00:38:18.215 --> 00:38:19.800 align:middle line:90%
is under question.

00:38:19.800 --> 00:38:24.832 align:middle line:84%
And this climate issue is going
to be particularly egregious.

00:38:24.832 --> 00:38:26.790 align:middle line:84%
And one of the things
that I've been working on

00:38:26.790 --> 00:38:31.610 align:middle line:84%
for about 15 years now is, when
the public realized the extent

00:38:31.610 --> 00:38:35.040 align:middle line:84%
to which they've been fooled,
deliberately fooled by this,

00:38:35.040 --> 00:38:37.410 align:middle line:84%
they'll start to say, we
don't believe in anything

00:38:37.410 --> 00:38:38.555 align:middle line:90%
you tell us.

00:38:38.555 --> 00:38:39.550 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Fool me once--

00:38:39.550 --> 00:38:40.350 align:middle line:90%
>>BALL: Yeah.

00:38:40.350 --> 00:38:43.050 align:middle line:84%
And that's the sad thing,
because as you said earlier,

00:38:43.050 --> 00:38:44.290 align:middle line:90%
pollution's a problem.

00:38:44.290 --> 00:38:45.620 align:middle line:90%
Environment's an issue.

00:38:45.620 --> 00:38:47.080 align:middle line:84%
We all care about
the environment.

00:38:47.080 --> 00:38:48.947 align:middle line:84%
But notice what
these people did.

00:38:48.947 --> 00:38:50.280 align:middle line:90%
They took the moral high ground.

00:38:50.280 --> 00:38:52.540 align:middle line:84%
We're the only guys that
care about the environment.

00:38:52.540 --> 00:38:53.540 align:middle line:90%
The rest you don't care.

00:38:53.540 --> 00:38:55.340 align:middle line:90%
How dare you do that!

00:38:55.340 --> 00:38:57.560 align:middle line:90%
But they wanted the dominance.

00:38:57.560 --> 00:39:00.570 align:middle line:84%
And by the way, one of the
countries that broke that cycle

00:39:00.570 --> 00:39:04.010 align:middle line:84%
was India, because the prime
minister of India, Modi,

00:39:04.010 --> 00:39:07.220 align:middle line:84%
went and I've worked with
Indian climatologists.

00:39:07.220 --> 00:39:08.870 align:middle line:90%
They know the signs very well.

00:39:08.870 --> 00:39:11.650 align:middle line:84%
And Modi looked at it and said,
OK, what you're telling us

00:39:11.650 --> 00:39:14.980 align:middle line:84%
is that there's a 2% chance
that the temperature might go up

00:39:14.980 --> 00:39:17.460 align:middle line:84%
by half a degree in
the next 50 years.

00:39:17.460 --> 00:39:20.740 align:middle line:10%
And the probability
of that is very slim.

00:39:20.740 --> 00:39:23.350 align:middle line:10%
And he said, we got
more important issues.

00:39:23.350 --> 00:39:25.080 align:middle line:84%
We've got people
starving to death.

00:39:25.080 --> 00:39:26.120 align:middle line:90%
Let's get the priority.

00:39:26.120 --> 00:39:29.142 align:middle line:84%
That took that moral high ground
away from these enviro bullies.

00:39:29.142 --> 00:39:30.600 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: And as
you said, the water

00:39:30.600 --> 00:39:32.160 align:middle line:84%
will become a huge
issue one day.

00:39:32.160 --> 00:39:33.980 align:middle line:10%
>>BALL: They're already
switching to that.

